all of these factors

25
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,720
affect how our immune
system is working,

26
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:17,210
and diseases push our immune
system every day to react,

27
00:01:17,210 --> 00:01:18,970
and our immune system
still has to keep

28
00:01:18,970 --> 00:01:22,120
at bay not attacking ourselves.

29
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,490
And an imbalance within
the immune system

30
00:01:24,490 --> 00:01:28,030
can cause diseases,
but likewise,

31
00:01:28,030 --> 00:01:32,440
allow the resolution of diseases
like pathogenic infections.

32
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:35,390
