00:11:30,100 --> 00:11:33,730
that recognize this part of
the protein of the virus.

253
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:35,365
So with that in
mind, actually, I

254
00:11:35,365 --> 00:11:37,240
would like to introduce
the next speaker that

255
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,460
is Arup Chakraborty, and
he will be digging more

256
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:43,946
into the B-cell response
and the biology of it.

257
00:11:43,946 --> 00:11:55,540
